{"tid":365188,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"陳嘉上fb撰文：政府主動製造社會撕裂","createTime":"2017-08-19T04:52:29.000Z","updateTime":"2017-08-20T14:05:58.000Z","uid":51271,"like":39,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":0,"replies":[{"pid":"67b998044fa7f34028c08248fcad82daa0c463dd","tid":365188,"uid":51271,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-08-19T04:52:29.000Z","msg":"<a href=\"http://hk.apple.nextmedia.com/realtime/news/20170819/57100214\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2Fhk.apple.nextmedia.com%2Frealtime%2Fnews%2F20170819%2F57100214&d=pd192AC71BAY2SsadnjqEWMi7htmHpjw5c1LyB4FCwE%3D&h=0c1a39fa\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=http%3A%2F%2Fhk.apple.nextmedia.com%2Frealtime%2Fnews%2F20170819%2F57100214&h=58692c20\" target=\"_blank\">http://hk.apple.nextmedia.com/realtime/news/20170819/57100214</a><br />\n<br />\n陳嘉上fb貼文：<br />\n一群年輕的公民因進入了被封閉的公民廣場被判重刑。若法院對以暴力執法的犯罪抱同一態度，我沒有問題。問題是我看到兩種態度，一時強調法律，一時強調包容，因政治立場而異。不要再問社會為何撕裂，因為這是政府主動製造的。有良心的人都無法為你們塗脂抹粉，太醜陋。<br />\n要求再審的是政府，不是嗎？和司法是否獨立無關。在這時候不發聲我過不了自己的關。這判决撕裂社會，對改善社會局面沒有好處。這是我看法。"},{"pid":"c881b930964b872e6fa1a726c42244d9e6cfc943","tid":365188,"uid":27664,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-08-19T07:09:47.000Z","msg":"都唔係第一日既事黎啦"},{"pid":"f414d6cca326a5639d2b83d580d66730b8ddb56d","tid":365188,"uid":61280,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-08-19T07:15:06.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>都唔係第一日既事黎啦</blockquote><br />\n<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><strong><span style=\"color: red;\">之前仲未搵夠，戲仲叫收得多冥紙嘛！！！！</span></strong></span><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/z.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/z.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"cbe89e1f62fc637ab480c8faa7d39a3d9294f5f2","tid":365188,"uid":29804,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-08-19T07:25:45.000Z","msg":"袁國強收左order<br />\n定自閹？"},{"pid":"aae98c473aa13b18342d5193acda8ed21bba8ca8","tid":365188,"uid":64072,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"r